  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Go Go Cosmo Cops! invites players to jump into the shoes of Leo and Jenny as they touch, flip and get rowdy in a battle against the resource-sucking Babools to save the earth. Just landed from outer-space, the Babools are threatening the Earth’s status quo by absorbing all its natural resources to build their giant towers. Using the ‘Accro Bracelet’ to give Leo and Jenny incredible super-powers, your job is to reach the top and take down the evil Babools by any means necessary.",
